data.text:
DURNING

According to the U.S. Census Bureau, Durning is ranked #26975 in terms of the most common surnames in America.

The Durning surname appeared 899 times in the 2010 census and if you were to sample 100,000 people in the United States, approximately 0 would have the surname Durning.

93.2% or 838 total occurrences were White.

2.4% or 22 total occurrences were of Hispanic origin.

2.1% or 19 total occurrences were Black.

1% or 9 total occurrences were of two or more races.
